node_modules
.env
    ```
4.  **Initialize Git and Push:** Create a new repository on GitHub, then run:
    
```bash
    git init
    git add .
    git commit -m "Initial commit: Project structure and dependencies"
    git remote add origin <your-github-repo-url>
    git push -u origin main
    ```

